subproject.description: The project promotes the concept of Corporate Social Responsibility among the Romanian SMEs sector stimulating interest in activities generating more than just a direct return, thus contributing towards long-term investments in human capital or the environment increasing competitiveness and ensuring a higher quality of life for the local community.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Introducing CSR to SMEs

title: Increased adaptability of Rom companies through CSR
